'''恐鱷屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Deinosuchus''），是種已滅絕大型[[鱷魚|鱷魚]]，屬於[[短吻鳄总科|短吻鳄总科]]，生存於[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]晚期的[[北美洲|北美洲]]東部海岸地區，約8,200萬到7,300萬年前。<ref name="lucas">{{cite journal
 |title=The giant crocodylian Deinosuchus from the Upper Cretaceous of the San Juan Basin, New Mexico 
 |journal=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin 
 |volume=35 
 |pages=247 
 |year=2006 
 |url=http://www.nmnaturalhistory.org/science/bulletins/35/sci_bulletin35_29.pdf 
 |format=pdf 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617095747/http://www.nmnaturalhistory.org/science/bulletins/35/sci_bulletin35_29.pdf 
 |archivedate=2009-06-17 
}}</ref>恐鱷的屬名在[[希臘文|希臘文]]意為「恐怖的鱷魚」，''δεινός''/''deinos''意為「恐怖」，''σουχος''/''suchos''意為「鱷魚」。

恐鱷是史上出現過最大型的鱷魚之一，体长9-10米，可能會以大型恐龍為食。目前發現的恐鱷化石主要以頭骨為主。根據近年研究，古生物學家對於恐鱷的身長估計值，較之前的估計值短。

==敘述==
===型態特徵===
[[Image:Deinosuchus_scutes_by_Hatcher.png|thumb]]，比現今鱷魚的皮內成骨更厚。由W.J. Holland繪製。]]
儘管恐鱷的體型很大，牠們的外形與現今的鱷魚相去不遠。<ref name="schwimmer-lifetimes">{{cite book|title=King of the Crocodylians: The Paleobiology of Deinosuchus|url=https://archive.org/details/kingofcrocodylia0000schw|last=Schwimmer|first=David R.|publisher=Indiana University Press|page=[https://archive.org/details/kingofcrocodylia0000schw/page/1 1]–16 (''The Life and Times of a Giant Crocodylian'')|year=2002|isbn=0-253-34087-X}}</ref>恐鱷具有類似[[短吻鱷|短吻鱷]]的寬廣口鼻部，口鼻部前端略為脹大。<ref name="schwimmer-lifetimes"/>牙齒厚而粗壯，嘴部後段的牙齒較短、鈍。<ref name="schwimmer-prey">Schwimmer, 167–192 (''The Prey of Giants'')</ref>

恐鱷的背部覆蓋者大型的[[皮內成骨|皮內成骨]]（Osteoderms），部份皮內成骨的形狀略呈半圓形。<ref name="holland">{{cite journal|title=''Deinosuchus hatcheri'', a new genus and species of crocodile from the Judith River beds of Montana|last=Holland|first=W.J.|journal=Annals of the Carnegie Museum|volume=6|year=1909|pages=281–294}}</ref><ref name="schwimmer-early">Schwimmer, 17–41 (''The Early Paleontology of Deinosuchus'')</ref>皮內成骨上有凹處與溝痕，被認為是某種軟組織的附著處。<ref name="schwimmer-early"/>有科學家認為恐鱷的皮內成骨與軟組織，可在這群大型動物在陸地上時，協助支撐巨大的身體。<ref name="schwimmer-early"/><ref name="schwimmer-size">Schwimmer, 42–63 (''The Size of Deinosuchus'')</ref>雖然恐鱷的體型巨大，但牠們在陸地上時可能行動敏捷，如同牠們的現代近親。<ref name="schwimmer-size"/><ref name="cloudsley-thompson">{{cite book|title=Ecology and Behaviour of Mesozoic Reptiles|url=https://archive.org/details/ecologybehaviour00clou|last=Cloudsley-Thompson|first=J.L.|publisher=Springer Science+Business Media|page=[https://archive.org/details/ecologybehaviour00clou/page/n49 40]–41|year=2005|isbn=3-540-22421-1}}</ref>

恐鱷具有骨質[[次生顎|次生顎]]，次生顎允許牠們的頭部沉浸在水面下時，可以透過水面上的鼻孔呼吸。<ref name="cloudsley-thompson"/>恐鱷的脊椎屬於前凹椎型，每節脊椎的前端凹陷，後端突出，脊椎與脊椎之間形成[[球窩關節|球窩關節]]。<ref name="colbert-bird">{{cite journal|title=[http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/handle/2246/2425 A gigantic crocodile from the Upper Cretaceous beds of Texas]|author=Colbert, Edwin H; Bird, Roland T.|journal=American Museum Novitates|volume=1688|year=1954|publisher=American Museum of Natural History}}</ref><ref name="foster">{{cite book|title=Jurassic West: The Dinosaurs of the Morrison Formation and Their World|last=Foster|first=John|publisher=Indiana University Press|year=2007|isbn=978-0-253-34870-8|page=150}}</ref>次生顎與前凹椎型脊椎，被認為是衍化的特徵，現代[[鱷目|鱷目]]也具有相同的衍化特徵。<ref name="cloudsley-thompson"/><ref name="rolleston-jackson">{{cite book|title=Forms of Animal Life|author=Rolleston, George; Jackson, William Hatchett|publisher=Oxford at the Clarendon Press|year=1870|page=392}}</ref>

根據科學家的估計，恐鱷的咬合力高達18,000[[磅|磅]]（80,000[[牛顿|牛顿]]）擁有目前已知地球陸地動物中最強大的咬合力。<ref name="schwimmer-lifetimes"/>而[[灣鱷|灣鱷]]的咬合力為4,200[[磅|磅]]（18,600[[牛顿|牛顿]]），是咬合力最大的現代動物。<ref name="erickson-et-al">{{cite journal|title=The ontogeny of bite-force performance in American alligator (Alligator mississippiensis)|journal=Journal of Zoology|volume=260|issue=3|pages=325|url=http://www.alligatorfarm.us/images/Research/Erickson%20et%20al.%202003.pdf|format=pdf|access-date=2009-01-05|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729035020/http://www.alligatorfarm.us/images/Research/Erickson%20et%20al.%202003.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

